2. What is Pyrite?
==================
Pyrite is an object oriented, dynamic programming language.

3. Status
=========
The current status of Pyrite is **NOT STABLE**, please don't use it for
productive projects.

4. Documentation
================
The raw documentation of Pyrite is placed in *doc/user/*.

For more information see http://pyrite-lang.org/.

5. Report Issues
================
See http://pyrite-lang.org/issues.

6. Build instructions
=====================
To build Pyrite (you'll need SCons (http://www.scons.org)) type:

    scons

For further instructions see http://pyrite-lang.org/install.

